{"tid":14200,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"提前過聖誕！雲格身邊有「古怪」... E-mail 此主題給朋友","createTime":"2016-11-30T11:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T11:46:18.000Z","uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4239e70c3bdea32e530c7cb73c6e478b1c6e1a7","tid":14200,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2016/11/30/f/fffea8e3e1510e5aa33e2f8f8726daa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2Ff%2Ffffea8e3e1510e5aa33e2f8f8726daa3.jpg&h=3d92cb0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這裝扮和表情&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2016/11/30/c/ca7616d293ee723a532f3755fa93ccd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2Fc%2Fca7616d293ee723a532f3755fa93ccd5.jpg&h=6606e586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕月份還沒到，但英超阿仙奴球會已經有了節日氣氛，在最新的一次記者會上，主教練雲格身邊出現了一些奇怪的「東西」。<br />\n<br />\n比拿連頭戴鹿角、卡蘇拿則在腦袋上套上了「褲子」，兩人表情嚴肅的坐在那裡，這本人就令人忍俊不禁。看起來，阿仙奴是想把這次記者會搞得輕鬆一點，增添了聖誕元素。<br />\n<br />\n整個記者會過程中，阿仙奴的師徒三人都表情嚴肅，一本正經的回答著問題，但雲格身邊這「哼哈二將」的裝扮，實在讓人沒法不笑，他們越嚴肅，現場的搞怪氣氛就越濃。<br />\n<br />\n(legion)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20161130/6608344/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsoccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2F1%2F20161130%2F6608344%2F&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=1be9e3e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20161130/6608344/</a>"},{"pid":"b90800cb63179599ea83706662471aceefe9ccfb","tid":14200,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"Email左去 joe@fevaworks.com <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}